"]}],"
",["$r","p",null,{"children":"What’s left is probably state."}],"
",["$r","p",null,{"children":"Let’s go through them one by one again:"}],"
",["$r","ol",null,{"children":["
",["$r","li",null,{"children":["The original list of products is ",["$r","strong",null,{"children":"passed in as props, so it’s not state."}]]}],"
",["$r","li",null,{"children":"The search text seems to be state since it changes over time and can’t be computed from anything."}],"
